name: iShares Core S&P U.S. Total Market Index ETF
longDescription: The fund seeks to provide long-term capital growth by replicating, to the extent possible, the performance of the S&P Total Market Index (the Index), net of expenses. The Fund will primarily invest in securities of one or more exchange-traded funds managed by BlackRock Canada or an affiliate (iShares ETFs) and/or U.S. equity securities.
